name: Highpoint Jetpack
description:
In Highpoint Jetpack, a little Free game that have a lot of fun to give to you, you are a lost astronaut who needs to escape from a floating platform who wants to kill you. Your only weapon is a Jetpack. Your target is the highest point of an infinite vertical space structure with obstacles. Don't be decentralized, the game wants it. Don't be nervous, the game is already nervous for you.

So, are you ready for your rise to the highest target in the universe ? Or are you affraid by your chances of dying. Good luck....

(Coming soon on the Google Play store)
